<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Arise, Yahweh! Attack them! Throw them down on their faces! Rescue my life from the wicked by your sword!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />Rescue me from men by your hand, Yahweh, from men of this world whose prosperity is in this life alone!</para>

<para style="q1">You will fill the bellies of your treasured ones with riches; they will have many children and will leave their wealth to their children.</para>
